{"tid":1251821,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"應該點樣去接受男朋友講大話","createTime":"2019-06-22T16:48:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-25T13:32:28.000Z","uid":146212,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e8f7f9e6e426e20c43d8491f46ccda901959f087","tid":1251821,"uid":146212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T16:48:55.000Z","msg":"同男朋友嗌交 我地一直講緊啲好傷感嘅嘢<br />\n佢同我講佢同屋企人出左去<br />\n但俾我發現佢同朋友出左去飲酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我可以原諒所有嘢 但我真係接受唔到佢呃我<br />\n由我踢爆佢 佢就冇再覆過我<br />\n我真係好心痛 我以為呢個世界只有佢唔會呃我 佢一直都係我最信任嘅人<br />\n我可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">我知你可能會睇到 咁你睇唔睇到我真係好傷心</span></span>"},{"pid":"c6ed1fd27eac4e1e76801d2d935524b5102767b3","tid":1251821,"uid":258566,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T16:51:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"293a23236e5fb7b9032c2cb8a293deda78ef1121","tid":1251821,"uid":256640,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T16:56:55.000Z","msg":"我明阿..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 發現對方呃自己真係會晴天霹靂<br />\nBTW而家佢都仲係冇覆你?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁樓豬想分手定繼續行落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3098fb900ba3a6e0a298629a527358f7a2aba905","tid":1251821,"uid":149357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T16:57:09.000Z","msg":"你係唔接受既 點解要自己接受？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b44c455199704ed8840bc5dcaeb9c5a3d3bf314","tid":1251821,"uid":47279,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T16:59:40.000Z","msg":"同男定女? 女就話姐 男嘅咁撚小事 咪撚7試嚟問啦屌你"},{"pid":"93ad9bc2788333f19b358a654b1ee8cecbd7d6ea","tid":1251821,"uid":62997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T17:08:23.000Z","msg":"你點樣踢爆佢